  but encountered an issue where clicking "Next Section" on the Intro page did
  not advance. 2. Report Generation: To expedite testing, the agent utilized a
  "Pre-fill & Jump to Report (Dev)" button, which successfully populated the
  form and eventually led to the report section. The PDF download functionality
  was tested and confirmed to be working, with a successful API call. 3. Admin
  Dashboard: The agent then navigated to the admin login page. After being
  redirected and unable to locate direct admin credentials, the agent tested the
  login error handling by entering an incorrect password, which successfully
  displayed an error message. 4. Navigation Issue Revisit: The agent returned to
  the questionnaire to further investigate the navigation issue, confirming that
  informational alerts in the IntroSection were present, and despite no console
  errors, the "Next Section" button remained unresponsive, preventing
  progression to the next section.'
